Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:18.71,CHT,,0,0,0,,"2065年12月13日 錄下夢境"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:32.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Every night, the same dream.\N{\rCHT}每天晚上 同樣的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:34.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,The same strange planet.\N{\rCHT}同樣奇怪的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,But why?\N{\rCHT}但是為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:37.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are they trying to tell me?\N{\rCHT}它們想告訴我什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:47.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's been thirty-four years since they arrived on this planet.\N{\rCHT}它們來到這個星球34年了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:49.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,And now the days passes, the survivors\N{\rCHT}被逼住在堡壘城市的倖存者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:53.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,forced to live in barrier Cities, do not live in fear.\N{\rCHT}沒有一天不是生活在恐懼中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:55.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have vowed to end that fear.\N{\rCHT}我發誓要解除這恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:58.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,I believe my dreams hold the key.\N{\rCHT}我相信我的夢就是鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:00.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,The question is,\N{\rCHT}問題是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:02.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,will I be in time to save the Earth?\N{\rCHT}我來得及拯救地球嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:54.23,CHT,,0,0,0,,"舊紐約市"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:57.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where are you?\N{\rCHT}你在哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is a restricted area.\N{\rCHT}這裡是禁區
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:08.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do not move!\N{\rCHT}別動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:10.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,What is she doing here, captain?\N{\rCHT}她在這兒幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:12.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but we are getting her out.\N{\rCHT}不知道 我們得帶她離開這
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:13.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're coming with us.\N{\rCHT}你得跟我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Behind you!\N{\rCHT}小心後面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!\N{\rCHT}站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Let's move, people.\N{\rCHT}該死 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Two, coming through the wall.\N{\rCHT}有兩隻從牆裡穿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:32.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hold your fire. Those tanks are flammable!\N{\rCHT}停火 那些桶是易燃物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:37.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ryan, Neil, let's go.\N{\rCHT}萊恩 尼爾 我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:44.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just what the hell do you think you are doing?\N{\rCHT}你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:45.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,There is a life-form in here.\N{\rCHT}這裡有一個生物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:48.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,- There hasn't been life here in years. - Well, there is now!\N{\rCHT}- 早就沒有了 - 現在有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:50.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Life-form or not, I'm taking you in.\N{\rCHT}不管有沒有 我都要帶你走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:51.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fine, Arrest me.\N{\rCHT}你就逮捕我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:53.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,But I'm not leaving without that life-form.\N{\rCHT}沒有這生物我不會離開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:58.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gonna be one of those days.\N{\rCHT}今天很倒楣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:16.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Captain, transport is not going to wait for us much longer.\N{\rCHT}隊長 運輸機是不會等我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I understand that.\N{\rCHT}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's in bad shape.\N{\rCHT}它的狀況很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:23.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please. Tell me we're not risking our necks for this plant.\N{\rCHT}拜託 我們不是為了這爛植物在冒生命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't even call it a plant. It's a weed.\N{\rCHT}真的都不算是植物 是雜草
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:27.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't even call it a weed.\N{\rCHT}我看連雜草都不算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:29.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,I need a minute to extract it.\N{\rCHT}等我一分鐘去萃取它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Miss, that's a minute we do not have.\N{\rCHT}我們連一分鐘都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:33.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid he's right about that, ma'am.\N{\rCHT}我恐怕他說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Phantoms! We have incoming.\N{\rCHT}有幽怪來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Captain, we need to get outta here.\N{\rCHT}隊長 我們得快走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:40.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Understood, sergeant.\N{\rCHT}知道了 中士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Could you hurry please, miss? - Done.\N{\rCHT}- 拜託你快點 - 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Captain. - Yes Neil.\N{\rCHT}- 隊長 - 什麼事 尼爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:46.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, I agree with the "let's get out of here" thing.\N{\rCHT}我覺得咱們應該趕快離開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:47.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Duly noted.\N{\rCHT}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:52.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can I have this please? Thank you.\N{\rCHT}請把那給我好嗎？謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:02.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We're surrounded. - No Shit!\N{\rCHT}- 我們被包圍了 - 廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:06.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, everybody. Just relax.\N{\rCHT}大夥兒別緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:08.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Captain, we got to get to higher ground.\N{\rCHT}我們得往高處逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Everyone, up top.\N{\rCHT}大夥兒快走 往上走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Go!\N{\rCHT}快走… 快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:20.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Transport, requesting immediate evac. - Affirmative.\N{\rCHT}- 請求立刻撤退 - 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:22.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Up here!\N{\rCHT}在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Captain!\N{\rCHT}隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,- They're right behind you! - Captain, come on!\N{\rCHT}- 他們就在你後面 - 隊長 快來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:37.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've got you!\N{\rCHT}我抓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:41.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You okay? - Yeah.\N{\rCHT}- 你沒事吧？- 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:43.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, everybody. Here they come.\N{\rCHT}好了 大夥兒 它們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,You okay?\N{\rCHT}你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:24.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're gonna be all right.\N{\rCHT}你不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:30.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can you give me one good reason why I shouldn't arrest you?\N{\rCHT}你可說說看我為什麼不該逮捕你？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:32.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,I am Dr. Aki Ross. I have clearance to be here.\N{\rCHT}我是阿琪羅絲博士 我有到此的許可證
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not unlimited clearance. And not without authorization.\N{\rCHT}不是無限制的許可 沒有授權
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Captain, I don't have time for this.\N{\rCHT}我沒時間跟你爭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:39.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you realize you've just risked the lives of my squad and me?\N{\rCHT}你明白我們在為你冒險嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:40.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look. I don't want to talk about it.\N{\rCHT}我不想再多說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:44.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,The fact of the matter is, it was worth the lives of you and your men.\N{\rCHT}事實是這值得你跟你的弟兄冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:45.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,You and your men?\N{\rCHT}什麼弟兄？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,- She thinks you are a man. - I think she's an idiot!\N{\rCHT}- 她以為你是男人 - 她是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:50.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I know you are not a man. - I think you are an idiot too.\N{\rCHT}- 我知道你不是男人 - 你也是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:51.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Very funny.\N{\rCHT}真是好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:52.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, I do wanna talk about it.\N{\rCHT}而我卻想說一說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:56.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,Did it ever occur to you that maybe we wouldn't volunteer to risk our lives...\N{\rCHT}你有沒有想過我們若有選擇…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,had we been given a choice?\N{\rCHT}是否會志願送死？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:00.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, nobody asked you to save me.\N{\rCHT}沒有人叫你們救我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:02.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't believe this. You have not changed a bit.\N{\rCHT}真不敢相信 你一點也沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:05.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gray?\N{\rCHT}葛雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:16.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, nice to see you too!\N{\rCHT}是啊 很高興再見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:31.91,CHT,,0,0,0,,"42號堡壘 城市：紐約市"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:15.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Welcome back, captain. - We're clean.\N{\rCHT}- 歡迎歸隊 隊長 - 我們沒有被感染
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's make sure of that, shall we?\N{\rCHT}我們最好確定一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,I hate getting scanned.\N{\rCHT}我最討厭接受掃描
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sir, these scanners are probably worse for us than the phantoms.\N{\rCHT}這掃描對我們來說比幽怪更糟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's no probable about it, captain.\N{\rCHT}隊長 有人杯疑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,These machines are suspected of causing sterility.\N{\rCHT}這玩意會造成不孕症
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:28.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I wanna have a little Neil junior to call me daddy someday.\N{\rCHT}我以後還想要個小尼爾叫我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:31.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That's a spooky thought. - Why are you always busting my chops?\N{\rCHT}- 太恐怖了吧 - 你幹嘛老找我碴？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:33.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,People, let's just do this thing, all right?\N{\rCHT}廢話少說 照做好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:35.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.\N{\rCHT}是 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes, sir. - Yes, sir.\N{\rCHT}- 是 長官 - 是 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.\N{\rCHT}好了 下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:53.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've gained some weight.\N{\rCHT}你變胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:56.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's called upper-body strength, Neil. Get a girlfriend.\N{\rCHT}這叫上肢力量 尼爾 找個女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:57.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm working on it.\N{\rCHT}我正在努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:01.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know my security rating allows me to bypass this.\N{\rCHT}我的保安級別給了我豁免權
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:03.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not today, it doesn't.\N{\rCHT}今天可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:08.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Something's not right. - About this mission?\N{\rCHT}- 有點不對勁 - 這項任務？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:10.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Or that woman? - Both.\N{\rCHT}- 還是那女的？- 都是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:10.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Next.\N{\rCHT}下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:15.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Listen, captain. I think... - I don't care what you think, doctor.\N{\rCHT}- 隊長 我想… - 我不管你怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:18.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're getting scanned just like everybody else.\N{\rCHT}你要跟別人一樣接受掃描
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh shit! - Captain\N{\rCHT}- 該死 - 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,- They got him. - There must be a mistake.\N{\rCHT}- 他受到了感染 - 一定是搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,You came in contact with a phantom, sir.\N{\rCHT}你接觸到了幽怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:34.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,Please remain calm. Administering treatment shield.\N{\rCHT}請保持冷靜 啟動治療防護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:36.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What level is he? - Blue.\N{\rCHT}- 什麼程度威染？- 藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:38.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,He will be code red in three and a half minutes.\N{\rCHT}3分半鐘後就紅色警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:42.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,We have to treat him now.\N{\rCHT}必須立刻替他治療
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:44.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but that's impossible.\N{\rCHT}對不起 這是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:46.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We'll transfer him to the treatment center. - There's no time for that.\N{\rCHT}- 我們要把他轉到治療中心 - 來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:52.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get him to the table.\N{\rCHT}把他抬上手術臺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hang in there captain.\N{\rCHT}你要挺住 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:10.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Locating pathogens.\N{\rCHT}搜尋病原體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:19.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jesus! Look at that thing.\N{\rCHT}天啊 你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:22.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,- How much more time? - Not enough.\N{\rCHT}- 還有多少時間？- 不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:23.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,When he reaches code red,\N{\rCHT}一旦達到紅色警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,the treatment shield won't be able to hold the alien particles.\N{\rCHT}這個罩子就無法控制病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:28.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Engaging bio-etheric laser.\N{\rCHT}啟動生化鐳射槍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What's going on? - Where did it go?\N{\rCHT}- 怎麼回事？- 它跑哪兒去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:50.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?\N{\rCHT}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:51.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,We've lost contact.\N{\rCHT}我們失去它的蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:53.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Infestation is moving deeper.\N{\rCHT}病毒往深處移動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:55.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Tracking... - There is no time.\N{\rCHT}- 追蹤 - 沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:57.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Tracking. - There is no time!\N{\rCHT}- 快追蹤 - 來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:58.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're gonna lose him.\N{\rCHT}他會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:01.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,His treatment shield is failing\N{\rCHT}防護罩失效了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:03.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Found it!\N{\rCHT}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:14.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on.\N{\rCHT}快呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:50.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's all right.\N{\rCHT}沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:54.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\N{\rCHT}不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:56.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,You'll be back to normal in no time.\N{\rCHT}你很快就會恢復的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:17:01.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Doctor, we need to scan you for infestation.\N{\rCHT}博士 你必須接受掃描看是否有感染
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,That won't be necessary.\N{\rCHT}這沒有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:05.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll take responsibility.\N{\rCHT}我願意負責
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:09.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, doc.\N{\rCHT}博士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thanks for saving him.\N{\rCHT}謝謝你救了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:18.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Are you all right? - Yeah, but the military has impounded my ship.\N{\rCHT}- 你沒事吧？- 沒事 軍方扣留我的船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:20.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's with her?\N{\rCHT}她是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:22.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's with her and the captain?\N{\rCHT}她跟隊長是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:24.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's with her and that stupid plant?\N{\rCHT}她跟那根爛草是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:27.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,What?\N{\rCHT}幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:37.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Forward me the phantom data and everything we've got of the five spirits collected so far.\N{\rCHT}把所有搜集到的五個靈魂的資料給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:38.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, doctor.\N{\rCHT}是 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:42.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Spirits? I thought we weren't supposed to use the S word.\N{\rCHT}靈魂？我以為我們不該用靈魂一詞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:44.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't get smart with me.\N{\rCHT}別跟我耍嘴皮子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:48.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now let's see if that plant does the trick.\N{\rCHT}我們看看那根植物有沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:55.31,CHT,,0,0,0,,"萃取植物能量波"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:57.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,"比對能量波"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:02.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's a match. We've found it.\N{\rCHT}完全符合 我們找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:03.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes,\N{\rCHT}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,the sixth spirit.\N{\rCHT}第六個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:08.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Your little scene today broke nearly every protocol.\N{\rCHT}你今天幾乎打破了每一個協議
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:11.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,How long do you think this would have survived outside the barrier?\N{\rCHT}你認為這根草在外還能活多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:14.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aki, you know there are elements in the Council and military\N{\rCHT}你可知那些議會和軍方有些份子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,just waiting for an excuse to shut us down.\N{\rCHT}都等著要關閉我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:20.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look. Twenty years ago, who discovered this energy in the phantoms?\N{\rCHT}聽著 誰在20年前找到幽怪的能量波？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:21.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,You.\N{\rCHT}是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:26.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,And who proved the same energy source existed in humans and every life form?\N{\rCHT}誰證明每種生物都有這能量？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:27.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,You.\N{\rCHT}是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:29.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,You made it possible to harness that energy\N{\rCHT}你使人能夠控制這種能量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:32.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,for OVO-packs, scanners, even the barrier.\N{\rCHT}把它用在生化電池 掃描機和堡壘城上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:34.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Council knows that.\N{\rCHT}議會很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:37.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,They trust you, Doctor. We're so close to proving it...\N{\rCHT}他們相信你 我們就快能證明…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:40.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,We still need this part and this one here.\N{\rCHT}我們仍然需要這部分 這一次在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:43.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Exactly! Two more pieces and we've solved the puzzle.\N{\rCHT}沒錯 只缺兩個就能解開謎底
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:45.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,We need to be free to find those pieces.\N{\rCHT}我們必須找到它們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want to show you something, Aki.\N{\rCHT}我給你看樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What is this? - Read.\N{\rCHT}- 這是什麼？- 讀一讀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:55.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,All life is born of Gaia and each life has a spirit.\N{\rCHT}所有生命都來自蓋亞而每個生命都有靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:58.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Each new spirit is housed in a physical body.\N{\rCHT}每個新靈魂都住在一個肉體內
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:18:59.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Doctor! - Go on.\N{\rCHT}- 博士 - 讀下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:04.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Through their experiences on Earth, each spirit matures and grows.\N{\rCHT}依據他們在地球上的經驗每個靈魂不斷成長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:07.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,When the physical body dies,\N{\rCHT}當肉體老死後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:12.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,the mature spirit, enriched by its life on Earth returns to Gaia.\N{\rCHT}經過生命洗禮的成熟靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:14.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Bringing with it the experiences,\N{\rCHT}將帶著這些經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,enabling Gaia to live and grow.\N{\rCHT}回歸于蓋亞讓蓋亞存活並成長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:19.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's my old diary.\N{\rCHT}這是我的舊日記
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:24.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wrote that fourty-three years ago when I was the age you are now.\N{\rCHT}43年前我還像你這個年紀的時候寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:27.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dr. Sid!\N{\rCHT}席德博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:29.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Remember what happened to Gallileo?\N{\rCHT}還記得伽利略的下場嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:31.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,They threw him in jail\N{\rCHT}他被關迸牢獄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:34.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,because he said the Earth was not the center of the universe.\N{\rCHT}因為他說地球不是宇宙中心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:36.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,That could happen to us.\N{\rCHT}這也可能發生在我們的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:39.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,Our ideas are unpopular, Aki.\N{\rCHT}我們的主張並不受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:43.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you have any notes or records, that could be used against you.\N{\rCHT}如果你有對自己不利的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:45.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Destroy them.\N{\rCHT}快毀掉它們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:47.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Keep them up here. - Right.\N{\rCHT}- 記在腦子裡 - 好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:51.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,And stay away from your friend, the captain.\N{\rCHT}離你朋友隊長遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:55.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,He saves your life, you save his life, this leads to that.\N{\rCHT}他救了你 你也救了他 別被沖昏了頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:19:56.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was young once too, you know.\N{\rCHT}我也年輕過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:59.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Doctor, there is a war going on.\N{\rCHT}博士 有一場戰爭正在進行中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:02.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,No one is young anymore.\N{\rCHT}現在再沒有年輕人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:06.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ladies and Gentlemen of the council,\N{\rCHT}各位議員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:09.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,could you please explain why?\N{\rCHT}你們能解釋為什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:12.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Zeus was completed a month ago.\N{\rCHT}宙斯炮一個月前完工
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:14.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,If we attack the meteor with this,\N{\rCHT}如果用來攻擊隕石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:17.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,we will eliminate the phantoms at their source.\N{\rCHT}就能徹底消滅幽怪的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:18.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,General Hein, calm down.\N{\rCHT}海恩將軍 請冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:21.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,At our last meeting, we voted six to two\N{\rCHT}上次我們六比二票決定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:24.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,to postpone using the Zeus cannon to attack the Leonid meteor.\N{\rCHT}暫緩利用宙斯炮攻擊裡奧尼德隕石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:28.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,We have reconvened today to vote on that very issue again.\N{\rCHT}這次要再投票表決
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:32.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, I'd like to ask the director of the Bio-Etheric Center to speak.\N{\rCHT}我想請生化能量中心主任發言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:35.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Dr. Sid, please. - Thank you.\N{\rCHT}- 席德博士 - 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:39.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,As you all know, the phantoms nest is in the Leonid meteor\N{\rCHT}大家知道幽怪巢穴是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:42.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,that landed here thirty-four years ago.\N{\rCHT}34年前墜落地球的裡奧尼德隕石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:44.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,What you see now,\N{\rCHT}現在所看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:47.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,are the records of every assault on the meteor to date.\N{\rCHT}是至今每次攻擊隕石的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:51.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Physical attacks have had utterly no affect.\N{\rCHT}猛烈攻擊完全無法造成損害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:55.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,This scene took place three months ago during a full scale bombardment.\N{\rCHT}三個月前進行全面性轟炸行動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:22:00.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now please note that the phantoms outside the meteor are indeed destroyed.\N{\rCHT}隕石外的幽怪確實被殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:04.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,However inside, many that were dormant come to life\N{\rCHT}但是潛伏在內的幽怪卻復蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.11,0:22:08.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,and as you see overall phantom density remains the same.\N{\rCHT}而你可以看到 幽怪的密度仍然跟以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:11.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,The newly risen aliens respond to the attack\N{\rCHT}當復蘇的幽怪遭到攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:14.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,by burrowing even deeper into the Earth.\N{\rCHT}便鑽入地球的更深層
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:17.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now this is very interesting to me, Dr. Sid.\N{\rCHT}這一點相當有趣 席德博士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:20.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because we see the same thing during surgery\N{\rCHT}我們使用生化鐳射
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.00,0:22:24.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,when using bio-etheric lasers on phantom particles.\N{\rCHT}切除幽怪病毒時也是這祥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:27.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Do we not? - Yes, indeed we do.\N{\rCHT}- 對不對？- 是的 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:30.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,You see the injured particles escape,\N{\rCHT}受傷的病毒脫逃後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:33.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,burying or digging themselves deeper into a patient's body,\N{\rCHT}會鑽入病患更深的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:35.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,and when we increase the laser power\N{\rCHT}我們為了消滅這些在更深層的病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.80,0:22:38.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,to destroy these deeper particles,\N{\rCHT}而加強鐳射量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.98,0:22:43.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,we have had incidents resulting in further injury to a patient,\N{\rCHT}我們曾意外地 造成病患更大的傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.10,0:22:44.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,and in some cases,\N{\rCHT}有時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:46.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,death.\N{\rCHT}會導致死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:48.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,And what exactly does that mean, doctor?\N{\rCHT}這代表了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.73,0:22:51.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,It means there's a very good chance\N{\rCHT}這代表一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.24,0:22:54.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,the beam from the Zeus cannon will burn the phantoms in the meteor.\N{\rCHT}宙斯炮會消滅幽怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.62,0:22:55.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Thank you.\N{\rCHT}正是這樣 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:22:58.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now, however, it also means\N{\rCHT}但是 那同時代表
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.19,0:23:01.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,that the beam energy may be too strong,\N{\rCHT}威力強大的鐳射炮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.37,0:23:02.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,injuring the Earth.\N{\rCHT}也會傷害地球
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:04.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Injure the Earth?\N{\rCHT}傷害地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.21,0:23:06.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,You mean the Gaia?\N{\rCHT}你是說蓋亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.43,0:23:10.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I mean... - You mean the spirit of the Earth.\N{\rCHT}- 我是說… - 你說的是地靈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:12.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\rCHT}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:15.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,The spirit of the Earth.\N{\rCHT}地球的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:18.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Did he just say what I think he said?\N{\rCHT}他說的是我想的那個意思嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:20.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What are you doing? - I know what I'm doing,\N{\rCHT}- 你在做什麼？- 我知道我在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:22.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,and whatever you do, keep your mouth shut.\N{\rCHT}你千萬別說話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.68,0:23:24.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous.\N{\rCHT}太荒謬了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:26.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Doctor, with all due respect.\N{\rCHT}恕我直言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:29.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Did you come here just to talk about some Gaia theory?\N{\rCHT}你是來高談蓋亞論嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:32.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,To tell us that the planet is alive?\N{\rCHT}你說地球是活的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.70,0:23:34.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,That it has a spirit?\N{\rCHT}它有靈魂？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.41,0:23:35.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's a fairy tale, doctor,\N{\rCHT}這是神話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:37.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,and I'm sorry, but we don't have time for that.\N{\rCHT}我們沒有時間再聽這些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.55,0:23:40.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,It is not a fairy tale, it is true.\N{\rCHT}這不是神話 這是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.14,0:23:45.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ah, so if I point a gun at the Earth and fire,\N{\rCHT}那麼 如果我拿著槍朝地上開一槍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.92,0:23:49.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not just making a hole on the ground, I'm killing the planet.\N{\rCHT}我不只射穿一個洞 還殺了地球
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.66,0:23:52.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dr. Sid, the Gaia theory has not been proven.\N{\rCHT}席德博士 蓋亞論未經證實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.27,0:23:54.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Even if Gaia does exist,\N{\rCHT}就算蓋亞存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:23:56.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,won't we still have to remove the phantoms?\N{\rCHT}我們不是也要消滅幽怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.23,0:23:59.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think if there's any chance of success,\N{\rCHT}如果有成功機會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:00.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,we should take it?\N{\rCHT}就要把握
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:02.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Don't you agree? - Of course I do.\N{\rCHT}- 你不同意嗎？- 當然同意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:05.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,But there is an alternative to the space cannon\N{\rCHT}但太空戰炮以外有另一個選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.76,0:24:06.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Another method?\N{\rCHT}有另一個方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:10.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes, a means of disabling the phantoms. - Please.\N{\rCHT}- 我有一個讓幽怪癱瘓的方法 - 請說
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.68,0:24:15.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,As we know the aliens display a distinct energy pattern.\N{\rCHT}據我們所知這些外星生物散發一種能量波
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.59,0:24:20.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now it is a fact that two opposing bio-etheric waves\N{\rCHT}只要把兩道相反的生化波
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.30,0:24:23.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,placed one over the other will cancel each other out.\N{\rCHT}重疊在一起 就能互相抵消
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.31,0:24:26.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,It is theoretically possible to construct a wave pattern\N{\rCHT}理論上可以重建一道能量波
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.55,0:24:29.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,in direct opposition to the phantom energy.\N{\rCHT}和幽怪的能量波完全相反
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.24,0:24:30.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We are currently assembling - Doctor.\N{\rCHT}- 我們正在製造這種能量波 - 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.62,0:24:32.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,such a wave and are nearing completion.\N{\rCHT}而且快要完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.32,0:24:33.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Members of the council\N{\rCHT}各位議員
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.11,0:24:36.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gathering plants and animals\N{\rCHT}搜集植物和動物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.38,0:24:41.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,from around the world to fight the phantoms is utter nonsense.\N{\rCHT}去對抗幽怪 筒直是無稽之談
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.69,0:24:45.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Zeus cannon is a proven, effective weapon.\N{\rCHT}宙斯炮證實是威力強大的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.44,0:24:48.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,It will kill phantoms.\N{\rCHT}它能消滅幽怪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.38,0:24:51.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can we afford to wait for some crazy invention,\N{\rCHT}我們能否等待得起一些瘋狂的發明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.52,0:24:55.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,some army of touchy-feely plants and animals,\N{\rCHT}一些憑直覺製造的動植物兵團
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.04,0:24:59.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,an invention that offers no solid evidence that it will destroy the aliens.\N{\rCHT}而卻沒有證據表明能摧毀這些外星生物？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.24,0:25:00.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,There is evidence.\N{\rCHT}當然有證據
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.87,0:25:02.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Our partially completed energy wave\N{\rCHT}目前半完成的能量波
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.92,0:25:05.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,has successfully stopped phantom particles\N{\rCHT}已經抑止幽怪病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.29,0:25:07.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,from spreading through a terminally infected patient.\N{\rCHT}在一名受感染病患身上擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.96,0:25:12.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Doctor, do you claim to have evidence that a terminal patient has been cured.\N{\rCHT}你可有證據能證明有垂死的患者痊癒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.18,0:25:15.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not cured. The wave is not complete.\N{\rCHT}不是痊癒 能量波尚未完成
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.35,0:25:20.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,But we've succeeded in containing the particles safely inside the patient.\N{\rCHT}但我們成功地控制了病毒的擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.57,0:25:23.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Where is the proof?\N{\rCHT}證據在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.77,0:25:25.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Here.\N{\rCHT}在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.73,0:25:42.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,You may've bought us some time, Aki. But I wonder at what cost?\N{\rCHT}你也許讓我們有多一點時間 但是代價呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.54,0:25:46.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I can't keep hiding in the background while you protect me.\N{\rCHT}我不能一直躲起來讓你維護我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.48,0:25:48.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want what life I have left to mean something.\N{\rCHT}我想在餘生有所貢獻
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.91,0:25:52.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,You listen to me. When we find the seventh and eighth spirits...\N{\rCHT}你聽我說 等我們找到第七和第八個靈魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.89,0:25:56.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,If we find them. What we need now is some luck.\N{\rCHT}我們需要運氣才可以找到它們
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.09,0:25:58.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Luck has nothing to do with it.\N{\rCHT}這跟運氣無關
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.12,0:26:01.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Faith and hard work, girl.\N{\rCHT}你要有信心和努力
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.31,0:26:04.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Cause I'll be damned if you're going to die before me.\N{\rCHT}我絕不會讓你比我先死
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.29,0:26:36.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Council decided to postpone firing the Zeus cannon.\N{\rCHT}議會決定暫緩發射宙斯炮
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.84,0:26:38.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,I guess I put on a good show.\N{\rCHT}我想我的表現還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.02,0:26:40.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Mind if I tag along?\N{\rCHT}介意我跟來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.52,0:26:42.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,You'll probably get bored.\N{\rCHT}你會覺得無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.53,0:26:57.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,So... what are you doing?\N{\rCHT}你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.17,0:27:03.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. You're giving me the silent treatment.\N{\rCHT}我知道了 你在跟我冷戰
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.17,0:27:06.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm scanning the city for the seventh spirit.\N{\rCHT}我要在市內搜索第七個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.60,0:27:21.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hurry up, Neil. - Relax serge, I almost got it.\N{\rCHT}- 尼爾 快點 - 輕鬆點 就快好了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.96,0:27:23.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?\N{\rCHT}你在搞什麼鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.18,0:27:25.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're just gonna strand them for a while.\N{\rCHT}我要把他們困在上面一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.16,0:27:28.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't look at me. It was his idea.\N{\rCHT}別看我 這是他的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.35,0:27:29.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,This was your idea?\N{\rCHT}這是你的主意？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.90,0:27:31.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're just helping the captain out a little.\N{\rCHT}我只是想幫隊長的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.63,0:27:34.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yeah, come on Jane, where's your sense of romance?\N{\rCHT}拜託 你的浪漫情調到哪兒去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.11,0:27:35.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,You've seen how the captain looks at her.\N{\rCHT}你看到隊長看她的眼神了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.82,0:27:42.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's "amore", baby.\N{\rCHT}那就是愛 寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.14,0:27:47.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What's going on? - It's probably just a glitch.\N{\rCHT}- 怎麼回事？- 可能只是個小故障
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.37,0:27:51.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Listen, Aki... - I'm still mad at you.\N{\rCHT}- 阿琪 聽著… - 我還在生你的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.96,0:27:55.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You're mad at me? - Leaving your helmet on, not telling me who you were?\N{\rCHT}- 你生我的氣？- 你戴著頭盔不說你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.50,0:27:57.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,That doesn't seem a little childish?\N{\rCHT}難道一點也不幼稚？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.66,0:28:00.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was just a little upset when you just packed up and left\N{\rCHT}你一聲不響就跑去宙斯太空站
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.27,0:28:02.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,for the Zeus station without saying a word.\N{\rCHT}讓我很生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.04,0:28:05.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well now you know what was going on, all right? - Yeah, now I know.\N{\rCHT}- 現在你知道是怎麼回事了吧？- 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.23,0:28:07.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,My operation had to be done in zero grav, okay?\N{\rCHT}我的任務必須在無重力狀態執行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.82,0:28:08.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fine!\N{\rCHT}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.24,0:28:11.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,And how about the fact that I was sent there on a job\N{\rCHT}我去太空站出公差
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.40,0:28:12.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,and you wouldn't even see me?\N{\rCHT}而你不肯見我？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.25,0:28:14.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was probably helping Dr. Sid collect spirit waves.\N{\rCHT}我大概是在搜集能量波
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.97,0:28:16.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Now I know. - So I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}- 我現在知道了 - 我很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.84,0:28:18.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, me too. So we're both sorry.\N{\rCHT}我也是 我們都很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.03,0:28:27.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,So will you tell me about them?\N{\rCHT}說來聽聽好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.08,0:28:29.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,About what?\N{\rCHT}說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.92,0:28:31.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,About the spirits you've collected.\N{\rCHT}你搜集的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.40,0:28:36.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,I was infected by a phantom during an experiment.\N{\rCHT}我在一項突驗中受到幽怪感染
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.92,0:28:38.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Normally no one could have survived.\N{\rCHT}通常沒人能活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.13,0:28:40.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,How did you?\N{\rCHT}你怎麼活下來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.48,0:28:43.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dr. Sid created a membrane around the infection,\N{\rCHT}席德博士用薄膜包住病原體
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.20,0:28:44.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,keeping me alive.\N{\rCHT}保住了我的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.78,0:28:46.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,So the first spirit wave was me.\N{\rCHT}所以第一個靈魂波就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.27,0:28:50.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,- The second was a fish. - A fish?\N{\rCHT}- 第二個是一條魚 - 魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.30,0:28:54.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,The third was a deer I found in a wildlife-preserve outside Moscow.\N{\rCHT}第三個是我在莫斯科野生保留區找到的一隻鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.94,0:28:56.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,The fourth was a bird.\N{\rCHT}第四個是一隻小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.78,0:28:59.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ever tried to track a sparrow from outer space?\N{\rCHT}你試過從外太空追蹤麻雀嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.86,0:29:00.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's no fun.\N{\rCHT}一點都不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.95,0:29:02.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,What am I saying? You probably would love that.\N{\rCHT}我在說什麼？你一定會很喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.92,0:29:04.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're right. I probably would.\N{\rCHT}你說得對 我可能會
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.24,0:29:07.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then there was that plant I collected from Time Square.\N{\rCHT}然後就是在時代廣場的那植物
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.60,0:29:09.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I thought that was number six. - What?\N{\rCHT}- 那不是第六個嗎？- 什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.66,0:29:10.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,You skipped one.\N{\rCHT}你跳過一個
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.35,0:29:18.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,The fifth was a little girl dying in a hospital emergency room.\N{\rCHT}第五個是醫院急診室裡垂死的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.37,0:29:21.95,ENG,,0,0,0,,I retrieved the sample in time, but she...\N{\rCHT}我及時採取了樣本 但是她…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.52,0:29:26.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,I told her everything had a spirit.\N{\rCHT}我跟她說萬物都有靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.81,0:29:31.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dogs, cats, trees, little girls, even the Earth.\N{\rCHT}狗 貓 樹木 小女孩 就連地球也有
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.06,0:29:36.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I told her that she wasn't dying, just returning to the Earth's spirit.\N{\rCHT}我告訴她她不是死 只是回歸到蓋亞
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.30,0:29:37.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,To Gaia.\N{\rCHT}也就是地靈
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.68,0:29:44.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,She... told me, that she was ready to die.\N{\rCHT}她跟我說她已準備好接受死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.48,0:29:51.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,She said I didn't have to make up stories to make her feel better.\N{\rCHT}她說我不必編故事來安慰她
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.76,0:29:58.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Only seven years old and ready to die.\N{\rCHT}她才七歲卻已準備好接受死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.94,0:30:00.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}我很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.50,0:30:05.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,I... have work to do. I have to find the seventh and eighth spirits.\N{\rCHT}我有工作要做 我必須找到第七和第八個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.28,0:30:08.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't... please...\N{\rCHT}別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.29,0:30:11.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't believe any of this, do you?\N{\rCHT}你一點都不信 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.24,0:30:15.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,I just... don't know, Aki.\N{\rCHT}我不知道 阿琪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.56,0:30:21.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is this why you've shut me out?\N{\rCHT}所以你才避著我？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.84,0:30:23.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,You should have told me.\N{\rCHT}你應該告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.51,0:30:27.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know how much time I have left.\N{\rCHT}我不知道我還能活多久
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.49,0:30:29.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Who does?\N{\rCHT}誰知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.46,0:30:37.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,I better get back to scanning.\N{\rCHT}我最好繼續我的搜尋
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.63,0:30:54.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Captain Edwards.\N{\rCHT}愛德華隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.44,0:31:00.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,You extracted a Dr. Ross from old New York, several days ago. Did you not?\N{\rCHT}幾天前你在舊紐約救回了羅絲博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.30,0:31:03.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yes sir. - What were your impressions of Dr. Ross?\N{\rCHT}- 是的 長官 - 你對她有什麼印象？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.72,0:31:06.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,She seemed very capable and determined, sir.\N{\rCHT}她看來非常有決心和能力
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.84,0:31:11.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,You and the Deep Eyes are being temporarily reassigned.\N{\rCHT}你的銳眼部隊暫時被重新分派
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.45,0:31:14.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,You will guard Dr. Ross when she re-enters the wasteland.\N{\rCHT}你們要保護羅絲博士回到荒原
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.07,0:31:16.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Understood, sir.\N{\rCHT}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.17,0:31:18.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,You don't understand yet, captain.\N{\rCHT}你還不明白 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.72,0:31:23.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Report any aberrant behavior in Dr. Ross to the major immediately.\N{\rCHT}她若有異常行為就向少校報告
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.34,0:31:24.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aberrant behavior, sir?\N{\rCHT}異常行為？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.64,0:31:27.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,The woman carries an alien infestation, captain.\N{\rCHT}她體內有外星生物感染
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.66,0:31:29.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,We don't know what it may be doing to her.\N{\rCHT}我們不知道對她有什麼影響
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.97,0:31:32.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,The alien presence could be affecting her judgment,\N{\rCHT}它可能影響她的判斷力
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.68,0:31:35.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,and may be manipulating the doctor for their very own purposes.\N{\rCHT}它們也許在操控她的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.87,0:31:39.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is the general suggesting that Dr. Ross is a spy?\N{\rCHT}將軍認為羅絲博士是間諜？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.30,0:31:44.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,The General is wondering why he's explaining himself to a captain.\N{\rCHT}將軍在奇怪為何他要跟一個隊長解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.90,0:31:47.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's had prolonged exposure to phantom tissue.\N{\rCHT}她曾長期接觸幽怪細胞
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.76,0:31:50.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,If this begins to manifest itself in any way,\N{\rCHT}如果它們侵佔她的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.32,0:31:52.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dr. Ross is to be placed under arrest,\N{\rCHT}立刻將她拘捕
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.86,0:31:55.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,and transported here for observation.\N{\rCHT}並把她帶回來接受現察
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.02,0:31:59.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,It is in fact, for her own good, captain.\N{\rCHT}這是為了她好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.01,0:32:01.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Of course, sir.\N{\rCHT}當然了 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.08,0:32:13.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Major, send some of our men to keep an eye on the good captain.\N{\rCHT}少校 派手下監視隊長的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.04,0:33:52.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm convinced that these dreams are some form of communication.\N{\rCHT}我深信這些夢境是一種交流方式
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.99,0:33:55.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Their message still eludes me.\N{\rCHT}雖然我不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.08,0:33:56.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,But they are coming faster now.\N{\rCHT}但它們越來越頻繁
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.60,0:33:58.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,And that can only mean one thing.\N{\rCHT}這代表一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.20,0:34:03.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,The phantoms inside me are beginning to win.\N{\rCHT}我就快被體內的幽怪侵佔了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.37,0:34:06.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Our target is 50 klicks left, at Tucson.\N{\rCHT}目標在圖森市以西50公里
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.65,0:34:07.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,Roger.\N{\rCHT}收到
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.40,0:34:09.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Phantom concentration? - Not good,\N{\rCHT}- 幽怪密度？- 情況不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.39,0:34:11.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,we've got big metas everywhere.\N{\rCHT}到處都有幽怪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.07,0:34:12.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,So it's gonna be a real picnic.\N{\rCHT}這下可好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.99,0:34:15.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stick close to me. No heroics today, okay?\N{\rCHT}跟著我 千萬別逞強 一切照規矩來
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.92,0:34:17.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Everything by the book.\N{\rCHT}照規矩來
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.08,0:34:19.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,By the book. Right.\N{\rCHT}照規矩來 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.00,0:34:24.86,CHT,,0,0,0,,"圖森荒原"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.53,0:34:28.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,If we dropped energy buoys here, here and here,\N{\rCHT}先在這些地方放置能量浮標
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.96,0:34:31.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,we should be able land, acquire the target...\N{\rCHT}我們就能取得目標
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.05,0:34:33.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,and get out before the phantoms even know we were there.\N{\rCHT}趁幽怪沒察覺趕快離開
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.32,0:34:35.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,And the buoys will attract the phantoms.\N{\rCHT}浮標會把幽怪引來？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.58,0:34:37.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Yeah. - For a while.\N{\rCHT}- 對 - 只是一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.31,0:34:49.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,So you're from the 307's, right?\N{\rCHT}你們是307支隊的？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.24,0:34:53.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Under General Hein? Ever done any wasteland recon before?\N{\rCHT}海恩將軍的部下？到荒原出過任務嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.18,0:34:55.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,It can get pretty ugly.\N{\rCHT}可能會很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.36,0:35:27.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Captain, rendezvous for evac at sector 6, coordinate 279.\N{\rCHT}隊長 待會撤離時到第六區 279座標會合
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.67,0:35:29.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Roger that. Stay alert for hostiles.\N{\rCHT}收到 保持警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.24,0:35:50.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Looks like they've taken the bait.\N{\rCHT}看來它們上當了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.36,0:36:09.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,The seventh spirit should be just beyond that line of wreckage.\N{\rCHT}第七個靈魂應該就在殘骸後面
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.68,0:36:12.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't see how any living thing could survive out here.\N{\rCHT}這兒怎麼會有生物生存下來？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.84,0:36:14.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll find out soon enough.\N{\rCHT}馬上就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.38,0:36:19.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,This was the phantom cleansing mission.\N{\rCHT}這原是幽怪掃蕩任務
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.76,0:36:22.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,It was supposed to end of war.\N{\rCHT}本來應該讓戰爭結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.80,0:36:27.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,My father's in here somewhere.\N{\rCHT}我父親也在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.30,0:36:31.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right.\N{\rCHT}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.09,0:36:33.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's move out, people.\N{\rCHT}我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.16,0:36:51.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll be damned.\N{\rCHT}我的天
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.76,0:36:53.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,A survivor.\N{\rCHT}一個生還者
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.93,0:36:55.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's it doing out here?\N{\rCHT}它在這兒幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.80,0:36:57.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hoping for life to return.\N{\rCHT}希望有重返的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.18,0:37:00.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is that our spirit, doc?\N{\rCHT}它是第七個靈魂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.62,0:37:03.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,No.\N{\rCHT}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.86,0:37:19.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're closing in on the life form.\N{\rCHT}我們正接近那個生物
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.88,0:37:22.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Distance? - Hard to say.\N{\rCHT}- 還有多遠？- 很難說
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.96,0:37:24.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're very close.\N{\rCHT}我們很接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.62,0:37:26.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything.\N{\rCHT}我什麼也沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.61,0:37:33.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna tell me it's him.\N{\rCHT}你不要告訴我那是他？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.90,0:37:35.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's impossible\N{\rCHT}不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.76,0:37:45.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's not the soldier. It's his OVO-pack.\N{\rCHT}不是他 是他的生化電池
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.85,0:37:47.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,How do you explain that?\N{\rCHT}不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.02,0:37:49.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Packs power our weapons, the barrier cities...\N{\rCHT}電池提供能量給我們的武器 堡壘城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.82,0:37:51.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean it's just bio-etheric energy.\N{\rCHT}那只是生化能量
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.82,0:37:54.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,And to create that energy, we use living tissue.\N{\rCHT}我們用活體組織在製造能量
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.40,0:37:55.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,Single cell organism.\N{\rCHT}單細胞生物
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.56,0:37:58.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You're telling me his backpack is the seventh spirit? - Yes.\N{\rCHT}- 他的電池就是第七個靈魂嗎？- 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.16,0:37:59.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,We have incoming.\N{\rCHT}幽怪來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.15,0:38:01.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Captain, do you read me? - What? say again?\N{\rCHT}- 隊長 收到嗎？- 再說一遍？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.82,0:38:04.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you read me, captain? We have incoming.\N{\rCHT}有收到嗎？幽怪來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.09,0:38:06.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ryan, get the soldier's pack.\N{\rCHT}萊恩 去拿那士兵的電池
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.50,0:38:25.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,I need a hand. Serge!\N{\rCHT}我需要支援 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.58,0:38:31.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Those buoys? - Yeah.\N{\rCHT}- 那些浮標？- 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.15,0:38:32.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,- They're not working. - Thank you.\N{\rCHT}- 壞了 - 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.84,0:38:38.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Are you all right? - Of course I am.\N{\rCHT}- 你沒事吧？- 當然沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.67,0:38:40.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's get the hell out of here!\N{\rCHT}咱們快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.36,0:38:46.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,Something's not right, this shouldn't be happening.\N{\rCHT}不應該這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.62,0:38:48.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Something's attracting them.\N{\rCHT}有什麼東西正把它們引來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.55,0:38:50.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aki!\N{\rCHT}阿琪
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.39,0:38:59.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,- They're right on us, sir. Closing in fast. - Jane, take the lead.\N{\rCHT}- 它們就快追上來了 - 簡 你打前鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.87,0:39:15.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fire in the hole!\N{\rCHT}我要開火了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.91,0:39:29.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get us out of here, Neil.\N{\rCHT}帶我們逃出去 尼爾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.04,0:39:32.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Sir, I would love to, but... - Just do it!\N{\rCHT}- 我也很想 但是… - 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.69,0:39:59.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Sir? - Ok, that's it!\N{\rCHT}- 長官？- 就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.31,0:40:03.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,That doesn't look good, captain.\N{\rCHT}她的情況不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.71,0:40:05.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,We have to get her to a hospital.\N{\rCHT}我們得送她去醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.66,0:40:09.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You have your orders, sir. - What the hell is going on here?\N{\rCHT}- 你知道命令的 - 這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.77,0:40:13.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dr. Ross is to be taken into custody, now sir!\N{\rCHT}我們必須立刻拘捕羅絲博士
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.52,0:40:19.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Lower your weapons. That's an order.\N{\rCHT}把武器放下 這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.50,0:40:22.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sir, we have no choice but to relieve you of your command.\N{\rCHT}我們別無選擇只能解除你的指揮權
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.08,0:40:24.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,I won't let you do this, soldier. You're gonna have to shoot me.\N{\rCHT}我不能讓你們這麼做 你得先殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.96,0:40:26.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stand down, captain!\N{\rCHT}隊長 別反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.59,0:41:27.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aki!\N{\rCHT}阿琪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.30,0:41:51.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hang on everyone!\N{\rCHT}大夥兒抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.21,0:42:01.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's enough! Hands where I can see them. Everyone. Now!\N{\rCHT}夠了 把手都舉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.40,0:42:13.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Deep Eyes hard to starboard!\N{\rCHT}銳眼部隊急右轉
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.24,0:42:27.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Neil, get us back to New York. Fast.\N{\rCHT}尼爾 快飛回紐約
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.28,0:42:40.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Deep Eyes are returning from the wasteland, sir.\N{\rCHT}銳眼部隊從荒原回來了 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.49,0:42:42.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Apparently there was an incident.\N{\rCHT}出了一個狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.40,0:42:46.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,It would seem the phantoms were attracted to Dr. Ross.\N{\rCHT}羅絲博士吸引了幽怪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.35,0:42:48.33,ENG,,0,0,0,,The crew barely escaped with their lives.\N{\rCHT}他們差點回不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.40,0:42:51.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,And sir... Captain Edwards is still in command.\N{\rCHT}但是長官… 愛德華隊長仍然有指揮權
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.44,0:42:54.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Issue an order.\N{\rCHT}下達命令
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.28,0:42:57.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,I want Edwards and Dr. Ross placed under arrest,\N{\rCHT}我要立刻逮捕愛德華隊長和羅絲博士
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.60,0:43:00.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,all research materials pertaining to Dr. Sid's wave theory\N{\rCHT}有關席德博士能量波論的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.86,0:43:02.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,are to be confiscated immediately.\N{\rCHT}全都給我沒收
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.83,0:43:05.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,That might not go over too well with the Council, sir.\N{\rCHT}議會不一定會接受
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.92,0:43:07.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,What a tragedy that would be.\N{\rCHT}那就太不幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.73,0:43:10.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is perfect, Major.\N{\rCHT}太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.57,0:43:12.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,The good captain has opened the door for us.\N{\rCHT}隊長給了我們一個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.40,0:43:16.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,By tomorrow morning, the Council would be at our feet.\N{\rCHT}明天他們會向我下跪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.30,0:43:18.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Thanking us for exposing the traitors in our midst.\N{\rCHT}感謝我揪出叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.44,0:43:21.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,And imploring us to save them from the phantoms.\N{\rCHT}而且從幽怪手上救出他們
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.68,0:43:28.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,How is she, doctor?\N{\rCHT}她的狀況怎樣 博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.15,0:43:32.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,- She is dying. - There must be something you can do.\N{\rCHT}- 她快死了 - 你一定還有辦法救她的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.80,0:43:35.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aki is fighting with only six of the eighth spirits.\N{\rCHT}阿琪只有六個靈魂為生命搏鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.28,0:43:38.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll have to implant the seventh directly into her chest plate.\N{\rCHT}我必須在她胸腔植入第七個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.56,0:43:41.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,It took a bullet. I think it might be damaged.\N{\rCHT}她中彈了 我想那胸腔可能受損了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.47,0:43:43.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,We have to repair this panel quickly.\N{\rCHT}我們必須立刻修復這一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.43,0:43:46.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Her vital signs are dropping.\N{\rCHT}她的生命跡象在減弱
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.76,0:43:49.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aki is slipping away from us.\N{\rCHT}阿琪快撐不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.03,0:43:54.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,She needs a sympathetic spirit to help hold her in this world.\N{\rCHT}她需要一個友善的靈魂説明挽留她
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.72,0:43:59.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I can think of no spirit better suited for that task than yours, captain.\N{\rCHT}最適合的人選就是你 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.80,0:44:03.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't understand. - You don't have to understand.\N{\rCHT}- 我不明白 - 你不必明白
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.66,0:44:05.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,You just be with her now.\N{\rCHT}你只要陪著她
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.89,0:44:08.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,You keep her here with us.\N{\rCHT}你挽留住她
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.94,0:45:03.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aki? Where are we?\N{\rCHT}阿琪 我們在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.63,0:45:05.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,On an alien planet.\N{\rCHT}在外星星球
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.50,0:45:07.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,How is that possible?\N{\rCHT}怎麼可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.73,0:45:10.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not entirely sure.\N{\rCHT}我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.80,0:45:12.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,You seem pretty calm.\N{\rCHT}你好像很冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.12,0:45:16.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've been having this dream every night for months.\N{\rCHT}我幾個月來每晚都有同樣的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.52,0:45:17.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dream?\N{\rCHT}夢境？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.05,0:45:20.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever it is.\N{\rCHT}我也不知道是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.14,0:45:24.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,You're really here, aren't you?\N{\rCHT}你真的在這兒 是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.52,0:45:28.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's happening to me?\N{\rCHT}我這是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.22,0:45:32.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dr. Sid is implanting the seventh spirit directly into your body.\N{\rCHT}席德博士正在將第七個靈魂直接植入你體內
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.00,0:45:35.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then you're my spiritual support.\N{\rCHT}那麼你是來精神支持我的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.00,0:45:38.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gray, how sweet of you.\N{\rCHT}葛雷 你對我真好
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.03,0:45:43.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look, I don't think you realize how serious the situation is.\N{\rCHT}我想你不知道情況有多嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.48,0:45:48.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Something you should see here, sir.\N{\rCHT}你最好過來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.71,0:45:59.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,And I am watching... what, major?\N{\rCHT}這是什麼玩意？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.34,0:46:02.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,It seems Dr. Ross has been recording her dreams.\N{\rCHT}羅絲博士一直在記錄她的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.05,0:46:07.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,And why would I be interested in ... her dreams?\N{\rCHT}她的夢境跟我有什麼… 關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.60,0:46:10.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is it. This is our evidence.\N{\rCHT}就是這個 這就是我們的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.05,0:46:13.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's under the influence of the phantoms.\N{\rCHT}她受到幽怪的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.32,0:46:23.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dr. Ross's dreams should be all the Council needs to authorize the firing of the Zeus cannon.\N{\rCHT}我要用這些來說服議會發射宙斯炮
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.18,0:46:26.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Council is content to hide, cowering inside this barrier\N{\rCHT}議會只顧著躲在堡壘城市
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.76,0:46:29.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,while the world dies a little more everyday.\N{\rCHT}而讓地球一天一天死去
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.44,0:46:32.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,believe they need a push in the right direction, major.\N{\rCHT}他們需要有人來推一把
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.38,0:46:34.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get together a group of your most trusted men.\N{\rCHT}召集你的心腹手下
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.12,0:47:29.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are they doing? Why are they staring at us?\N{\rCHT}他們在做什麼？它們為什麼盯著我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.56,0:47:31.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Not at us.\N{\rCHT}它們盯著的不是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.48,0:48:23.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, captain.\N{\rCHT}歡迎回來 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.22,0:48:27.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Is it over?\N{\rCHT}結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.48,0:48:29.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,How is she, Doctor?\N{\rCHT}她怎麼樣 博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.71,0:48:32.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,She's gonna be fine. But this is only temporary.\N{\rCHT}她沒事 但這只是暫時的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.64,0:48:35.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll need to find the eighth and final spirit to cure her.\N{\rCHT}一定要找到最後的第八個靈魂才能救她
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.29,0:48:42.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aki, can you hear me?\N{\rCHT}阿琪 你聽到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.22,0:48:45.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,I've finished it.\N{\rCHT}我做完夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.00,0:48:47.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know what it means.\N{\rCHT}我知道它的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.09,0:48:50.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know what the phantoms really are.\N{\rCHT}我知道幽怪到底是什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.92,0:48:56.10,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nobody move! You're all under arrest!\N{\rCHT}別動 你們被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.24,0:49:07.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,We have them, sir.\N{\rCHT}我們抓住他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.89,0:49:10.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sir?\N{\rCHT}長官？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.60,0:49:12.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,My wife and daughter.\N{\rCHT}我太太和女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.83,0:49:19.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Were killed by phantoms in the San Francisco barrier when the city was attacked.\N{\rCHT}在三藩市堡壘城市被幽怪害死了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.92,0:49:21.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,Did I ever tell you that?\N{\rCHT}我有沒有提過？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.11,0:49:25.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,I try to imagine what...\N{\rCHT}我試著想像她們的感受…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.00,0:49:32.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,what that must've been like, seeing everyone around you fall over dead, for no apparent reason.\N{\rCHT}看著身邊的人無緣無故死去
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.85,0:49:37.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then at the end, feeling something next to you.\N{\rCHT}最後感覺有什麼在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.16,0:49:41.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Invisible... touching you.\N{\rCHT}無形的… 觸碰你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.81,0:49:44.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Reaching inside your body and...\N{\rCHT}伸入你的軀體內…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.76,0:49:51.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You've lost family, haven't you? - Yes, sir.\N{\rCHT}- 你也失去了家人 對吧？- 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.96,0:49:54.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's why I trust you.\N{\rCHT}所以我才信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.89,0:49:56.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,All of you.\N{\rCHT}信任你們每個人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.64,0:49:59.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,You know what must be done.\N{\rCHT}你們知道必須怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.48,0:50:05.99,CHT,,0,0,0,,"堡壘主控中心"
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.67,0:50:08.51,CHT,,0,0,0,,"解除安全密碼"
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.32,0:50:10.96,CHT,,0,0,0,,"圍場被破"
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.48,0:50:15.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Major, arrest these men.\N{\rCHT}少校 逮捕他們
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.41,0:50:18.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Take it easy - Stand up. Go.\N{\rCHT}- 別亂來 - 起來 走
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.29,0:50:22.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,You are relieved of your post. Don't ask questions.\N{\rCHT}你們被解職了 別多問
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.15,0:50:27.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Reduce power to sector 31.\N{\rCHT}降低31段的防護能源
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.12,0:50:29.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sir, you do realize that the phantoms...\N{\rCHT}你可知道幽怪會…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.45,0:50:34.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,What I realize, major, is that we must force the Council to take action against the enemy.\N{\rCHT}據我所知我們要逼迫議會消滅敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.53,0:50:44.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,25 percent of energy pipe alpha. Redirected.\N{\rCHT}第一個電管百分之二十五的能量改向
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.48,0:50:48.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Lowering power output to sector 31.\N{\rCHT}降低31段防護能力
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.58,0:50:52.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,Barrier breach in sector 31, General. They're coming through now.\N{\rCHT}31段防護罩失效 幽怪進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.86,0:50:56.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh I think we can easily handle a few phantoms in a contained space.\N{\rCHT}我們可以在密封的空間殺死幾隻幽怪
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.15,0:50:58.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Relax, major.\N{\rCHT}別緊張 少校
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.51,0:51:01.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,When this night's over, you're going to be a hero.\N{\rCHT}明天一早你就成為英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.56,0:51:07.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Aki, I don't think... - You were in my dream, Gray. You saw it.\N{\rCHT}- 我不… - 當時你也在 你也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.63,0:51:10.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's just it. I'm not sure what I saw. How can you be?\N{\rCHT}我不確定我看到的 你怎麼能確定？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.28,0:51:12.81,ENG,,0,0,0,,Captain, please. Let her continue.\N{\rCHT}隊長 請你讓她說下去
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.99,0:51:16.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right. Why do you think, we've never been able\N{\rCHT}我們為什麼一直沒辦法確定
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.24,0:51:19.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,to determine a relationship between the human size phantoms\N{\rCHT}人形大小的幽怪
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.21,0:51:21.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,and the giant ones roaming the wastelands.\N{\rCHT}跟龐大幽怪的關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.56,0:51:25.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, doc, but... what freakin relationship?\N{\rCHT}不好意思 它們能有什麼鬼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.42,0:51:29.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean you got your human size phantoms and your creepy caterpillary phantoms\N{\rCHT}有人形幽怪 噁心的毛蟲幽怪
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.85,0:51:32.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,and your flying phantoms. And let's not forget my personal favorite...\N{\rCHT}會飛的幽怪 還有不要忘了我個人最喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.94,0:51:34.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,the big fat giant phantoms...\N{\rCHT}巨大肥胖的幽怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.75,0:51:36.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Down, boy. - He's right.\N{\rCHT}- 冷靜點 - 他說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.60,0:51:38.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you've spend as much time in the field as we have,\N{\rCHT}要是你常跟它們周旋
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.80,0:51:42.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,you know there is no relationship. It's like a zoo out there.\N{\rCHT}就知道它們沒有關係 就像動物園一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.60,0:51:46.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Precisely. I think the giant ones are like our whales or elephants.\N{\rCHT}沒錯 大幽怪就像是我們的鯨魚或大象
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.40,0:51:50.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,But why would an invading army bring a bunch of whales and elephants along for the ride?\N{\rCHT}但是侵略部隊帶鯨魚大象來幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.68,0:51:53.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Unless their ship was some kind of a crazy Noah's ark.\N{\rCHT}除非那是外星人的諾亞方舟？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.20,0:51:59.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,We've always assumed that the meteor was intended as a form of transportation.\N{\rCHT}我們一直以為隕石是交通工具
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.39,0:52:00.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it wasn't.\N{\rCHT}也許它不是
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.67,0:52:03.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,The meteor is a chunk of their planet that got thrown into space...\N{\rCHT}隕石只是一塊他們炸毀星球後…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.47,0:52:05.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,when they destroyed their world.\N{\rCHT}被扔到太空中的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.12,0:52:09.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,But how could they survive the trip across outer space on a hunk of rock?\N{\rCHT}它們怎麼能活著通過太空？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.06,0:52:11.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,They didn't.\N{\rCHT}它們沒有存活
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.13,0:52:17.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is all beginning to make a creepy kind of sense.\N{\rCHT}這好像有點恐怖的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.84,0:52:19.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,What do you think about all this, captain?\N{\rCHT}你覺得呢？隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.06,0:52:23.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think that explains why we never had a chance.\N{\rCHT}我認為這就解釋了為何我們會贏不了它們
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.89,0:52:27.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,All our strategies are based on one assumption.\N{\rCHT}我們的戰略都是基於一種假設
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.73,0:52:30.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,That we were fighting alien invaders.\N{\rCHT}我們在和外星侵略者作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.76,0:52:32.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Think of the dream, Gray.\N{\rCHT}你想想夢境 葛雷
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.72,0:52:34.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,How they died.\N{\rCHT}它們是怎麼死的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.08,0:52:36.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Since then, all they've known is suffering.\N{\rCHT}從那之後 它們只知道痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.90,0:52:39.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,They're not an invading army.\N{\rCHT}它們不是侵略兵團
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.15,0:52:40.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,They're ghosts.\N{\rCHT}它們是鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.52,0:52:43.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,How many phantoms?\N{\rCHT}有多少幽怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.14,0:52:47.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,- More than enough to convince the Council, sir. - Excellent.\N{\rCHT}- 足夠可以說服議會的 - 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.26,0:52:50.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Sound an alert. Send a squad out to eliminate them. - Yes sir.\N{\rCHT}- 示警 立刻派部隊去消滅它們 - 是 長官
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.75,0:52:52.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,Alert Status: Full Deployment.\N{\rCHT}全面警戒 全體動員
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.50,0:52:55.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sir, I have numerous phantom contacts.\N{\rCHT}有很多幽怪來襲
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.59,0:52:58.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Well, of course you do. - Outside of sector 31, sir.\N{\rCHT}- 當然了 - 它們在31段以外
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.46,0:53:00.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,And moving at incredible speed.\N{\rCHT}而且行動迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.14,0:53:02.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Major, what the hell is going on here?\N{\rCHT}這到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.14,0:53:03.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,They are in the pipes.\N{\rCHT}它們在管道中
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.58,0:53:06.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,They're moving with the bio-etheric energy flow.\N{\rCHT}跟著生化電力一起流竄
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.38,0:53:07.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.\N{\rCHT}不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.72,0:53:10.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,No living thing could survive in those pipes.\N{\rCHT}沒有東西可以在這些管子中存活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.13,0:53:13.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, we've got a big one heading this way,\N{\rCHT}一隻巨大幽怪正朝這兒沖來
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.27,0:53:14.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,meta class, sir.\N{\rCHT}是米達種的 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.24,0:53:23.77,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh my god...\N{\rCHT}我的天
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.48,0:53:26.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hold your fire!\N{\rCHT}別開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.46,0:54:14.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,What have I done?\N{\rCHT}我做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.07,0:54:37.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come on, Neil. We need to find a way out.\N{\rCHT}尼爾 我們得逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.01,0:54:39.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now you're our man, think!\N{\rCHT}你是高手 快想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.69,0:54:43.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,Captain, these walls are titanium alloy. And the bars are pulse-sonic lasers.\N{\rCHT}這是鈦合金鋼柱和鐳射光束
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.69,0:54:46.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's not like I can just wave a magic wand and...\N{\rCHT}我不能就這樣施展個魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.27,0:54:53.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Neil, I'm impressed. - That makes two of us.\N{\rCHT}- 我很佩服你 - 我也很佩服自己
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.07,0:54:56.06,CHT,,0,0,0,,"立刻前往最近的撤退區"
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.75,0:54:59.12,CHT,,0,0,0,,"立刻前往最近的撤退區"
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.16,0:55:02.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,I think we should proceed to the nearest evacuation facility.\N{\rCHT}我們應該立刻前往最近的撤退區
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.56,0:55:30.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Here they come. - But the others... Dr. Sid!\N{\rCHT}- 它們來了 - 但別人呢？席德博士
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.14,0:55:32.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Deep Eyes will take care of him. Come on!\N{\rCHT}銳眼部隊會保護他
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.17,0:55:42.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's happening? Why can we see them now?\N{\rCHT}怎麼回事 我們怎麼會看得見它們？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.41,0:55:45.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,They must be carrying a residual charge from passing through the barrier.\N{\rCHT}它們身上殘留了防護罩的電力
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.57,0:55:51.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,Behind you!\N{\rCHT}小心後面
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.97,0:56:55.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,All aboard, captain.\N{\rCHT}全都上車了 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.38,0:58:04.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,We need to find my ship.\N{\rCHT}我們需要找到我的太空船
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.67,0:58:07.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,If it was towed inside the city, it would be in the military hangar.\N{\rCHT}如果它被拖到了這個城市 它一定在軍事停機棚
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.58,0:58:09.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's a big "If".\N{\rCHT}這個假設範圍可夠大的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.18,0:58:19.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,Look out!\N{\rCHT}小心
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.28,0:58:29.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Get us out of the platform. - You got it.\N{\rCHT}- 快開到月臺 - 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.46,0:58:49.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, now what?\N{\rCHT}現在呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.45,0:58:51.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We're going through the station. - What?\N{\rCHT}- 我們要穿越車站 - 什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.68,0:58:53.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Captain, with all due respect...\N{\rCHT}恕我直言…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.37,0:58:55.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Excuse me, captain... - The Station...\N{\rCHT}- 對不起 隊長… - 車站…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.44,0:58:57.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're going through it.\N{\rCHT}我們要衝過去
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.12,0:58:58.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's the only way.\N{\rCHT}那是唯一的出路
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.16,0:59:02.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,So I gather this will be somewhat of a rough ride.\N{\rCHT}我猜這會是一個巔簸之旅？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.89,0:59:05.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Doc, you've got a talent for understatement.\N{\rCHT}博士 你挺會猜測的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.45,0:59:07.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hang on, everybody.\N{\rCHT}大家坐好了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.72,0:59:32.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,Doc?\N{\rCHT}博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.44,0:59:38.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Interesting.\N{\rCHT}有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.10,0:59:41.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Anybody hurt? - Captain!\N{\rCHT}- 有人受傷嗎？- 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.65,0:59:48.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Oh God! Talk to me, serge.\N{\rCHT}老天 快說話 中士
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.88,0:59:50.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ouch.\N{\rCHT}好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.35,0:59:51.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Give me a hand, Jane. - Right.\N{\rCHT}- 幫我個忙 - 好
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.68,0:59:52.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, wait!\N{\rCHT}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.68,0:59:53.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're risking further injury.\N{\rCHT}這祥會加重他的傷勢的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.92,0:59:55.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,We need the proper tools to cut him out.\N{\rCHT}我們需要適合的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.95,0:59:57.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,They're in my ship.\N{\rCHT}工具在我船上
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.66,1:00:02.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,No! No, Doc. No drugs. - Captain...\N{\rCHT}- 不 我不要打針下藥 - 隊長？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.09,1:00:03.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,You heard the man.\N{\rCHT}你聽見他說的了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.24,1:00:06.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll find the ship and we'll be back for you.\N{\rCHT}我們會找到船然後回來找你
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.25,1:00:07.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I'll stay with him. - Me too.\N{\rCHT}- 我留下來陪他 - 我也是
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.93,1:00:09.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nobody's staying.\N{\rCHT}誰都別留下來
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.89,1:00:13.05,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Just give me a gun. - You got it.\N{\rCHT}- 給我一把槍 - 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.12,1:00:14.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Give him a weapon.\N{\rCHT}把槍給他
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.59,1:00:15.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do it!\N{\rCHT}快點
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.06,1:00:19.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll be back for you, sergeant.\N{\rCHT}我們會回來救你的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.31,1:00:21.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,You hear me?\N{\rCHT}聽到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.76,1:00:25.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,I hear you, captain. Now get out of here.\N{\rCHT}聽到了 隊長 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.28,1:00:26.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's move out.\N{\rCHT}我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.79,1:01:20.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,A quad-axle ATV. This is good.\N{\rCHT}四軸越野車 太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.24,1:01:24.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,It can be used to retrieve Ryan and transport him safely here.\N{\rCHT}我們可以去把萊恩救回來
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.84,1:01:27.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,However we'll need to replace these spent fuel cells.\N{\rCHT}但是要換電池
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.06,1:01:30.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,There could be some live OVO-packs in the hangar.\N{\rCHT}停機棚一定有新的電池
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.78,1:01:32.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right, Jane. Check the hangar.\N{\rCHT}你去停機棚
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.41,1:01:34.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Neil, get us ready for takeoff.\N{\rCHT}尼爾 去啟動引擎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.06,1:01:36.19,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aki and Dr. Sid prep the Quattro.\N{\rCHT}阿琪和席德博士啟動越野車
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.24,1:01:38.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the tower and rotate the air-tray.\N{\rCHT}我去塔臺開啟平臺
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.70,1:01:41.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,This city maybe lost, but we are not.\N{\rCHT}城市也許淪陷了 但我們不會
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.71,1:01:43.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's do this thing and get the hell out of here.\N{\rCHT}我們一定會逃出去
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.73,1:01:57.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Gray... Be careful. - You too.\N{\rCHT}- 小心點 - 你也是
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.98,1:02:41.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.\N{\rCHT}太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.88,1:02:58.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Neil, do you read me?\N{\rCHT}尼爾 收到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.41,1:03:00.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Loud and clear, captain.\N{\rCHT}收到了 隊長
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.47,1:03:02.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,This baby will fly itself.\N{\rCHT}這玩意是全自動的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.81,1:03:11.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,Flight path is set.\N{\rCHT}航道設定好了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.24,1:03:12.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Beginning rotation.\N{\rCHT}轉動平臺
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.27,1:03:18.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wow, stop, stop the air-tray. We have a problem.\N{\rCHT}停下來 有問題
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.76,1:03:21.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm reading an impound tractor still attached to the prow of the ship.\N{\rCHT}太空船連著一輛被拖吊的牽引車
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.56,1:03:23.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can you disengage it from the cockpit?\N{\rCHT}你能從駕駛艙解開它嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.21,1:03:26.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, sir. Permission to go outside and detach the coupling.\N{\rCHT}請讓我到外面解開它
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.36,1:03:28.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do it!\N{\rCHT}快去
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.12,1:03:41.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,There's the problem.\N{\rCHT}問題在那裡
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.47,1:03:53.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,The controls are locked, naturally.\N{\rCHT}控制板被鎖住了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.09,1:03:57.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jane, let me ask you something.\N{\rCHT}讓我問你一件事
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.76,1:03:59.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,You think we're gonna get outta here alive?\N{\rCHT}咱們逃得出去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.68,1:04:01.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean I'm wondering if anybody has gotten out.\N{\rCHT}不知道以前有沒有人逃出去
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.11,1:04:04.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,You think anyone's made it this far?\N{\rCHT}你覺得有人逃了這麼遠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.81,1:04:07.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,You think this eighth spirit stuff is really gonna work against the phantoms?\N{\rCHT}這第八個靈魂真的能消滅幽怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.82,1:04:10.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,I mean, what if it's all a bunch of mumbo-jumbo?\N{\rCHT}也許全都是胡扯呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.87,1:04:14.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jane, do you mind if we stop talking?\N{\rCHT}簡 拜託你別嘮叨了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.19,1:04:16.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to concentrate here.\N{\rCHT}讓我專心吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.67,1:04:30.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,What's happening down there.\N{\rCHT}下面發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.73,1:04:32.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nothing we can't handle.\N{\rCHT}我們都可以處理好的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.10,1:04:47.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Neil, what's your status? - Almost there.\N{\rCHT}- 尼爾 怎麼樣？- 快好了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.41,1:04:51.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,- I want you two back inside. - We're fine, sir.\N{\rCHT}- 你們快回去 - 放心
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.21,1:04:53.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jane is negotiating with extreme prejudice.\N{\rCHT}簡在展開強硬政策
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.90,1:04:55.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Talk to me, Jane.\N{\rCHT}簡 快回答
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.87,1:04:59.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,No problem here, Captain.\N{\rCHT}我沒問題
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.38,1:05:07.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes! Captain, we are good to go.\N{\rCHT}好了 可以出發了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.70,1:05:31.70,ENG,,0,0,0,,No!\N{\rCHT}不
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.01,1:05:49.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jane, get out of there.\N{\rCHT}簡 快走
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.31,1:05:51.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get out of there now! Go!\N{\rCHT}快走呀 趕快走
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.47,1:05:54.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jane, get the hell out of there!\N{\rCHT}簡 快點離開那兒
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.99,1:05:56.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,Jane!\N{\rCHT}簡
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.87,1:06:24.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,The shield is powered and ready.\N{\rCHT}防護罩啟動了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.80,1:06:26.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Where are you going? - To the cockpit.\N{\rCHT}- 你要去哪兒？- 去駕駛艙
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.33,1:06:27.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,The ship is set on autopilot.\N{\rCHT}船已設置自動駕駛儀
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.92,1:06:29.88,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're in countdown to liftoff.\N{\rCHT}我們要倒數發射了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.95,1:06:33.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, wait. It's too dangerous. Aki!\N{\rCHT}等一下 這太危險了 阿琪
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.16,1:06:59.13,ENG,,0,0,0,,Over here, you son of a bitch!\N{\rCHT}我在這兒 臭怪物
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.65,1:08:14.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ryan!\N{\rCHT}萊恩
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.75,1:08:28.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gray, do you read me? What's happening?\N{\rCHT}葛雷 你收到嗎？怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.05,1:08:31.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,You and Sid are getting out of here now.\N{\rCHT}你和席德快走
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.16,1:08:34.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,- No! We can't just leave everyone. - Everyone's dead.\N{\rCHT}- 不 我不能丟下大家 - 大家都死了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.81,1:08:36.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm not leaving without you.\N{\rCHT}我不能丟下你
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.46,1:08:37.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.69,1:08:39.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,But you don't have a choice.\N{\rCHT}你別無選擇
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.47,1:08:41.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Aki.\N{\rCHT}再見 阿琪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.73,1:09:22.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gray, come on!\N{\rCHT}葛雷 快上來
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.02,1:11:28.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,I just...\N{\rCHT}我很想…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.08,1:11:33.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,I wish I could believe they're in a better place.\N{\rCHT}我很想相信他們到了更好的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.45,1:13:17.43,CHT,,0,0,0,,"宙斯太空站"
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.64,1:13:20.15,CHT,,0,0,0,,"確認目的地 獲准前進"
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.26,1:13:45.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,I enlarged the scanning perimeter\N{\rCHT}我擴大了搜索範圍
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.20,1:13:48.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,to include an area that we have previously overlooked.\N{\rCHT}包括了一個之前沒找過的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.27,1:13:50.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,The impact crater.\N{\rCHT}隕石坑
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.21,1:13:53.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's a strange place to find the eighth spirit.\N{\rCHT}好奇怪的第八個靈魂藏身處
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.36,1:13:55.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, really. Quite astonishing.\N{\rCHT}是的 很不可思議
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.24,1:13:57.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,But nothing could survive in there except phantoms.\N{\rCHT}那兒除了幽怪沒別的生物可以存活下來
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.76,1:13:58.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Precisely.\N{\rCHT}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.10,1:14:02.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Which suggests that the eighth spirit is a phantom spirit.\N{\rCHT}也就是說第八個靈魂是幽怪
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.59,1:14:04.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't explain it at the moment.\N{\rCHT}我目前不能解釋
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.22,1:14:05.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,- But once we get down there... - Wait!\N{\rCHT}- 但只要我們下去… - 等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.72,1:14:07.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,- You'll understand... - Wait, doctor.\N{\rCHT}- 就會明白的… - 慢著 博士
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.80,1:14:09.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's a one-way trip.\N{\rCHT}這可是一去不回
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.50,1:14:12.83,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, I expected that's how you would evaluate our chances.\N{\rCHT}是的 我就知道你是這麼評估我們的機會的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.83,1:14:15.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,- What, am I wrong? - No, no, no, I agree. We probably\N{\rCHT}- 我說錯了嗎？- 沒錯 我同意 我們也許
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.06,1:14:19.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,won't live long enough to extract the eighth spirit from the crater.\N{\rCHT}無法活著把第八個靈魂萃取回來
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.48,1:14:21.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Then why should we even try it?\N{\rCHT}那為什麼還要去試？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.02,1:14:23.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Because we don't need to extract the eighth spirit.\N{\rCHT}因為我們不必把第八個靈魂萃取回來
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.44,1:14:25.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,If we can't bring the final spirit here.\N{\rCHT}如果我們無法找到最後一個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.44,1:14:28.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,We can go there and complete the wave inside the crater.\N{\rCHT}就直接在隕石坑完成能量波
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.32,1:14:29.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes. Exactly.\N{\rCHT}一點也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.77,1:14:32.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,And how do we do that... exactly?\N{\rCHT}我們該怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.38,1:14:34.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can construct a device,\N{\rCHT}我會設計一個裝置
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.04,1:14:38.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,that would attach to Aki's chest plate to gather the eighth spirit and then...\N{\rCHT}裝在阿琪身上讓她採集第八個靈魂…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.77,1:14:41.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then what?\N{\rCHT}然後呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.37,1:14:42.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,And then we wait...\N{\rCHT}然後就等著瞧…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.16,1:14:44.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,and see what happens.\N{\rCHT}會發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.05,1:14:46.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's it?\N{\rCHT}就這祥？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.92,1:14:49.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's your plan? We wait and see what happens?\N{\rCHT}你的計畫就是等著瞧？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.12,1:14:50.43,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\rCHT}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.60,1:14:52.92,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.\N{\rCHT}太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.13,1:14:54.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well I got my own plan.\N{\rCHT}我也有計劃
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.80,1:14:56.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,We keep scanning the surface from orbit,\N{\rCHT}繼續從軌道掃描地球表面
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.49,1:14:59.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,and maybe we'll find a compatible spirit somewhere else.\N{\rCHT}也許能在別處找到相容的第八個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.29,1:15:00.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aki?\N{\rCHT}阿琪？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.02,1:15:02.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,I say we go in.\N{\rCHT}我建議我們下去
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.86,1:15:11.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,General Hein, you're clear for docking to zero-one-alpha.\N{\rCHT}海恩將軍 你可連接零一開端
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.48,1:15:35.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,What caused the barrier to fail, General Hein?\N{\rCHT}海恩將軍 請問防護罩為什麼會失靈？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.94,1:15:38.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm afraid it was only a matter of time\N{\rCHT}這是遲早會發生的事
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.97,1:15:42.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,before the phantoms developed an immunity to our barriers.\N{\rCHT}幽怪對防護罩產生抵抗力
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.68,1:15:45.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,But I am relieved to see that you and the rest of the Council\N{\rCHT}但是我很高興看到你和議員們
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.15,1:15:48.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,were able to evacuate to Houston, without incident.\N{\rCHT}都安全地撤逃到休士頓
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.07,1:15:51.40,ENG,,0,0,0,,It was a terrible loss suffered this evening.\N{\rCHT}今晚的事件是一場悲劇
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.96,1:15:55.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,The Council had reconsidered your proposal to fire the Zeus cannon.\N{\rCHT}議會重新考量了你對發射宙斯炮的提議
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.26,1:15:56.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,I see.\N{\rCHT}很好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.86,1:15:59.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,We are transmitting the access codes to you now.\N{\rCHT}我們現在就把發射密碼傳給你
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.88,1:16:02.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,And General...\N{\rCHT}將軍…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.76,1:16:05.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,best of luck to us all.\N{\rCHT}祝大家好運
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.72,1:16:10.57,ENG,,0,0,0,,Prepare to fire the cannon.\N{\rCHT}準備發射宙斯炮
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.57,1:16:12.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,The target, sir?\N{\rCHT}目標是？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.29,1:16:15.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,The phantom crater.\N{\rCHT}幽怪隕石坑
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.20,1:16:27.22,CHT,,0,0,0,,"裡海山脈 幽怪隕石坑"
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.83,1:16:45.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,Preparing to drop in three, two, one.\N{\rCHT}準備降落 3 2 l
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.62,1:16:52.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,Powering the shield.\N{\rCHT}啟動防護罩
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.12,1:16:57.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Okay, we are over the meteor.\N{\rCHT}我們在隕石坑上方
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.13,1:16:58.86,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you have it in sight, doctor?\N{\rCHT}你看到了嗎 博士？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.58,1:17:01.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,There are so many of them.\N{\rCHT}有太多幽怪了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.48,1:17:05.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,Wait.\N{\rCHT}等等
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.60,1:17:06.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes!\N{\rCHT}是的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.51,1:17:10.06,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm tracking the eighth spirit moving along the crater's surface.\N{\rCHT}我追蹤到在隕石坑表面的第八個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.27,1:17:13.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,All right. Now let's take a closer look.\N{\rCHT}好 那就靠近一點
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.48,1:17:55.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ready to fire in three minutes.\N{\rCHT}準備三分鐘後發射
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.58,1:17:57.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,OVO-packs at maximum.\N{\rCHT}開到最強電力
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.47,1:17:59.85,ENG,,0,0,0,,Transferring plasma flow to auto.\N{\rCHT}轉換自動流量
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.90,1:18:02.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Counter-thrusters are engaged.\N{\rCHT}反制推動器準備好了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.06,1:18:03.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Lox flow de-coupled.\N{\rCHT}開啟流管鎖
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.79,1:18:05.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Status is green.\N{\rCHT}一切正常
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.15,1:18:08.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,We have something on the radar over the impact site, sir.\N{\rCHT}我們發現隕石坑有動靜
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.75,1:18:12.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's her.\N{\rCHT}是她
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.41,1:18:13.75,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sir?\N{\rCHT}長官？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.96,1:18:16.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Just a traitor under the influence of the enemy.\N{\rCHT}是被敵人控制的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.64,1:18:18.27,ENG,,0,0,0,,Continue the countdown.\N{\rCHT}繼續倒數計時
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.51,1:18:21.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,We'll take them all out at the same time.\N{\rCHT}我們一起把它們消滅掉
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.02,1:18:28.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're closing on the phantom. Contact in 30 seconds.\N{\rCHT}接近幽怪了 三十秒後接觸
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.28,1:18:31.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,Target locked.\N{\rCHT}目標鎖定
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.09,1:18:34.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ready to fire on your command.\N{\rCHT}等待你下令發射
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.57,1:18:41.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's a match. It's a perfect match.\N{\rCHT}完全符合 能量波完全符合
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.24,1:18:43.23,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Target scanners ready, sir. - Fire!\N{\rCHT}- 準備好了 - 發射
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.44,1:19:19.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,What was that?\N{\rCHT}那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.56,1:19:22.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's the Zeus. They're firing on the crater.\N{\rCHT}是宙斯炮 他們向隕石坑發射宙斯炮
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.09,1:19:24.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aki, Captain, are you all right?\N{\rCHT}你們沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.36,1:19:26.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,A little shaken. Stand by.\N{\rCHT}只是嚇了一跳 請待命
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.11,1:19:30.14,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sid, the eighth spirit is not on our scanner. Do you have it?\N{\rCHT}我在掃描器上看不到第八個靈魂 你看得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.99,1:19:32.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,The eighth spirit...\N{\rCHT}第八個靈魂…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.82,1:19:35.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,has been destroyed.\N{\rCHT}被消滅了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.69,1:19:37.52,ENG,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do now?\N{\rCHT}現在該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.53,1:19:39.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,Nothing. This mission is over.\N{\rCHT}沒怎麼辦 任務結束了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.90,1:19:41.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We have to get out of here. - Incoming!\N{\rCHT}- 我們要離開這 - 襲擊來了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.75,1:20:15.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,What is that?\N{\rCHT}那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.55,1:20:18.12,ENG,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna get us out of here, you better do it now.\N{\rCHT}我們要走就得趁現在
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.85,1:20:32.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Hold on!\N{\rCHT}堅持住
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.16,1:20:43.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,I can't hold on to you.\N{\rCHT}我堅持不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.78,1:20:49.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Unable to maintain altitude...\N{\rCHT}無法維持高度…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.67,1:21:00.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Emergency landing procedures.\N{\rCHT}啟動緊急降落程式
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.58,1:21:26.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Come in. Come in, please.\N{\rCHT}快回答我
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.57,1:21:29.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aki, Gray, can you hear me?\N{\rCHT}阿琪 葛雷 你們收到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.42,1:21:31.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sid, I need to talk to the station.\N{\rCHT}博士 我要和他們對話
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.87,1:21:33.63,ENG,,0,0,0,,Can you patch us through?\N{\rCHT}你能幫我接去太空站嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.80,1:21:37.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?\N{\rCHT}那是什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.44,1:21:38.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't know, sir.\N{\rCHT}我不知道 長官
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.12,1:21:40.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,Incoming message, sir.\N{\rCHT}有資訊傳送進來 長官
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.69,1:21:44.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,General Hein, you must cease fire immediately.\N{\rCHT}海恩將軍 請你立刻停火
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.25,1:21:48.60,ENG,,0,0,0,,What you're looking at in the crater is the living spirit of an alien's home world.\N{\rCHT}你所看到的是外星人的地靈
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.83,1:21:51.55,ENG,,0,0,0,,The planet was destroyed and part of it landed here.\N{\rCHT}它們的星球被毀滅後降落到地球
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.56,1:21:54.73,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is not an invasion. It never was.\N{\rCHT}這從一開始就不是侵略行動
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.78,1:21:55.53,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.\N{\rCHT}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.53,1:21:59.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,And... and what we have been fighting all this time, doctor? Ghosts?\N{\rCHT}那我們都在跟什麼打仗？鬼魂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.31,1:22:00.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes,\N{\rCHT}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.32,1:22:03.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,spirits that are confused, lost and angry.\N{\rCHT}感到迷惑 失落和憤怒的鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.44,1:22:06.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, right? And these spirits are coming out of this Gaia thing\N{\rCHT}是嗎？這些鬼都是來自蓋亞
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.97,1:22:08.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,General Hein, you have to listen...\N{\rCHT}將軍 你要聽我說…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.81,1:22:10.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Alien Gaia, Earth Gaia...\N{\rCHT}外星蓋亞 地球蓋亞…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.41,1:22:12.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,Doctor, even if I believed in such nonsense,\N{\rCHT}就算我相信這些
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.57,1:22:14.89,ENG,,0,0,0,,the fact remains the Earth is under attack\N{\rCHT}地球仍然受到侵略者的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.89,1:22:18.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,from an aggressor who must be destroyed at all costs.\N{\rCHT}它們必須被不擇手段的消滅掉
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.17,1:22:20.91,ENG,,0,0,0,,The cost may be the entire planet, sir.\N{\rCHT}代價是地球也會被毀滅
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.92,1:22:24.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Firing on the alien Gaia will only make it stronger.\N{\rCHT}外星蓋亞遭到攻擊後會更強大
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.11,1:22:26.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, since you're under the alien's influence, doctor...\N{\rCHT}既然你是受到外星人的影響
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.09,1:22:27.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,I will take your protest to mean that,\N{\rCHT}我會接受你的提議
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.80,1:22:30.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,we are in fact pursuing the correct course of action. So,\N{\rCHT}我們會採取正確的行動 所以…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.78,1:22:32.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,I suggest you take your last few moments\N{\rCHT}我建議你珍惜最後的時光
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.99,1:22:35.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,and prepare to meet your Gaia.\N{\rCHT}等著去見你的蓋亞吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.50,1:22:38.46,ENG,,0,0,0,,Continue to fire until the invader has been destroyed.\N{\rCHT}繼續開火直到完全殲滅侵略者
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.00,1:23:17.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,General, the system is overheating, sir.\N{\rCHT}將軍 系統過熱了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.47,1:23:19.66,ENG,,0,0,0,,We are going to hit again and again...\N{\rCHT}我要不斷的攻擊…
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.66,1:23:21.47,ENG,,0,0,0,,and keep on hitting it, until it's dead.\N{\rCHT}直到它們全死光
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.47,1:23:24.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,But sir, we're not even sure if it's having any effect on the creature.\N{\rCHT}我們不確定這是不是有沒有效
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.30,1:23:25.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,No effect?\N{\rCHT}有沒有效？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.64,1:23:27.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,We've got them on the run, soldier.\N{\rCHT}它們已經走投無路了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.06,1:23:30.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is our moment of victory.\N{\rCHT}勝利就快來臨
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.65,1:23:32.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I order you to fire.\N{\rCHT}我命令你發射
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.20,1:23:35.87,ENG,,0,0,0,,- The system won't allow us to fire again. - We'll see about that.\N{\rCHT}- 系統無法繼續發射 - 等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.37,1:23:40.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Our shield is out. We're sitting ducks in here. Come on.\N{\rCHT}防護罩失效 這是等死了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.77,1:24:04.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is not a good place to be.\N{\rCHT}這不是個可以留下的好地方
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.50,1:24:15.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?\N{\rCHT}那是什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.47,1:24:18.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,- That's not what I think it is, is it? - Yes! It's Gaia.\N{\rCHT}- 和我想像的一樣嗎？- 是 這就是蓋亞
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.30,1:24:20.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,This is definitely not a good place to be.\N{\rCHT}這的確不是個可以留下的好地方
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.75,1:24:25.71,ENG,,0,0,0,,- Hey, are you all right? - I'm fine.\N{\rCHT}- 你沒事吧？- 沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.85,1:24:27.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have to talk to Dr. Sid.\N{\rCHT}我得跟席德博士通話
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.99,1:25:09.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Sid, do you read me?\N{\rCHT}席德 你收到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.32,1:25:12.32,ENG,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. I'm still here.\N{\rCHT}我還在 說吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.73,1:25:17.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,We're looking at Gaia. Do you hear me, Sid? Gaia!\N{\rCHT}蓋亞就在我們眼前 聽到了嗎？蓋亞
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.37,1:25:21.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,I... I think this explains why the eighth spirit appeared here.\N{\rCHT}這解釋了為什麼第八個靈魂會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.38,1:25:23.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\rCHT}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.19,1:25:25.82,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it.\N{\rCHT}沒錯 這就對了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.95,1:25:28.69,ENG,,0,0,0,,A phantom must have changed into the eighth spirit\N{\rCHT}一隻幽怪接觸到我們蓋亞產生的生命
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.69,1:25:32.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,when it touched a new life born from our own Gaia.\N{\rCHT}於是它轉變成第八個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.17,1:25:35.18,ENG,,0,0,0,,If so, it would have been given a different energy signature\N{\rCHT}所以它的能量波
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.18,1:25:37.84,ENG,,0,0,0,,that set it apart from the other phantoms.\N{\rCHT}才會跟別的幽怪不同
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.25,1:25:40.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ah, you two could not have hoped\N{\rCHT}這是找到新而相容
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.54,1:25:44.54,ENG,,0,0,0,,for a better location to find a new compatible spirit.\N{\rCHT}第八個靈魂的最佳地點
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.78,1:25:46.67,ENG,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do, don't move.\N{\rCHT}無論如何都不要動
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.68,1:25:48.36,ENG,,0,0,0,,Stay right where you are.\N{\rCHT}留在原地
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.09,1:25:53.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,Staying right where we are may not be as easy as it sounds.\N{\rCHT}留在這裡可不像聽上去那麼容易
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.17,1:25:56.17,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot any of them.\N{\rCHT}別對它們任何一個開槍
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.28,1:25:59.37,ENG,,0,0,0,,You could very well destroy our last hope.\N{\rCHT}你很可能會毀掉我們最後一線希望
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.37,1:26:01.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,And what do you suggest I do, Doctor?\N{\rCHT}你要讓我怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.30,1:26:02.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Ask them to play nice?\N{\rCHT}叫它們乖一點嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.72,1:26:07.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,Combat strategy is your area of expertise, captain, not mine.\N{\rCHT}戰略是你的專長 隊長 不是我的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.01,1:26:10.97,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have a reading here in the fissure, Do you see it?\N{\rCHT}我在裂口這裡收到了能量波 你看到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.31,1:26:14.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, a compatible spirit.\N{\rCHT}是的 那是相容的第八個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.11,1:26:15.93,ENG,,0,0,0,,It must be very near you.\N{\rCHT}它一定離你很近
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.95,1:26:18.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well, which one is it?\N{\rCHT}那麼 哪一個才是？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.44,1:26:19.68,ENG,,0,0,0,,Which one?\N{\rCHT}哪一個？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.72,1:26:23.50,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm having difficulty narrowing it down, just a moment please.\N{\rCHT}我還看不出來 請等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.50,1:26:29.00,ENG,,0,0,0,,Doctor, it's getting crowded in here. Aki, we don't have much time.\N{\rCHT}這裡變得太擠了 阿琪 沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.02,1:26:32.03,ENG,,0,0,0,,Aki... Aki!\N{\rCHT}阿琪… 阿琪
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.21,1:28:03.34,ENG,,0,0,0,,With the hope of new life,\N{\rCHT}抱著新生命的希望
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.61,1:28:06.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,has Gaia changed the phantom within?\N{\rCHT}蓋亞改變了內在的幽怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.80,1:28:14.44,ENG,,0,0,0,,I have it.\N{\rCHT}我找到了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.24,1:28:22.74,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gray, get in here. I need you.\N{\rCHT}快進來 我需要你
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.87,1:28:25.21,ENG,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me, Sid?\N{\rCHT}你聽到了嗎 席德？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.23,1:28:27.26,ENG,,0,0,0,,The wave pattern is complete.\N{\rCHT}能量波完成了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.32,1:28:30.09,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, I read you. This is wonderful.\N{\rCHT}收到了 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.52,1:28:34.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,I don't see how you could have found the final spirit.\N{\rCHT}我不知道你怎樣找到了最後一個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.08,1:28:35.90,ENG,,0,0,0,,It found me, doctor.\N{\rCHT}是它找到了我
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.76,1:28:39.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, my word.\N{\rCHT}我的天
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.88,1:28:42.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,I see now...\N{\rCHT}我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.88,1:28:44.28,ENG,,0,0,0,,I understand.\N{\rCHT}我懂了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.28,1:28:46.72,ENG,,0,0,0,,Well I don't understand. What the hell is going on?\N{\rCHT}我不懂 到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.72,1:28:49.15,ENG,,0,0,0,,Give me your OVO-pack. I need to project the completed wave.\N{\rCHT}給我你的電池 我需要它來完成發射能量波
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.16,1:28:52.41,ENG,,0,0,0,,- But we'll be defenseless. - Just do it.\N{\rCHT}- 我們會變得手無寸鐵 - 你照做吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.76,1:28:54.62,ENG,,0,0,0,,I hope you know what you're doing, Aki.\N{\rCHT}我希望你們知道在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.64,1:28:57.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We can use the shield to project the wave. - What?\N{\rCHT}- 我們要用防護罩發射能量波 - 什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.36,1:29:00.79,ENG,,0,0,0,,Dr. Sid's theory was right. I have it, the eighth spirit.\N{\rCHT}席德博士說得對 我已得到了第八個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.00,1:29:02.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'm cured, Gray.\N{\rCHT}我痊癒了 葛雷
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.51,1:29:04.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you have the final spirit?\N{\rCHT}你確定你得到了最後一個靈魂？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.38,1:29:06.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. I'm sure.\N{\rCHT}我很確定
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.01,1:29:07.39,ENG,,0,0,0,,But how? How can you know that?\N{\rCHT}你怎麼知道？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.39,1:29:09.31,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, a phantom told me.\N{\rCHT}別擔心 一隻幽怪告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.34,1:29:11.07,ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, great.\N{\rCHT}是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.18,1:29:13.08,ENG,,0,0,0,,That's it. Shield on.\N{\rCHT}好了 啟動防護罩
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.29,1:29:22.51,ENG,,0,0,0,,It's not working. We have to do something before it's too late.\N{\rCHT}沒有用 我們要趕快想辦法
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.59,1:29:25.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,If this doesn't work, then it's already too late.\N{\rCHT}這若是沒用的話 一切都太遲了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.56,1:29:35.11,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gray... trust me.\N{\rCHT}相信我
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.08,1:30:01.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,I'll blast you all to hell.\N{\rCHT}我要把你們都打下地獄
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.43,1:30:11.64,ENG,,0,0,0,,No! No!\N{\rCHT}不
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.07,1:30:16.22,ENG,,0,0,0,,Get down!\N{\rCHT}趴下來
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.04,1:30:31.47,CHT,,0,0,0,,"警告 系統超載"
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.47,1:30:32.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know.\N{\rCHT}我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.48,1:30:34.40,CHT,,0,0,0,,"警告 系統超載"
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.40,1:30:35.58,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know!\N{\rCHT}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.02,1:30:38.16,ENG,,0,0,0,,I know!\N{\rCHT}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.62,1:30:42.38,ENG,,0,0,0,,But it must be done.\N{\rCHT}但一定要這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.66,1:31:26.76,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fire!\N{\rCHT}發射
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.76,1:31:28.35,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fire, damn you!\N{\rCHT}發射 快呀
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.34,1:31:30.65,ENG,,0,0,0,,Fire!\N{\rCHT}發射
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.36,1:32:23.49,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gray?\N{\rCHT}葛雷？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.33,1:32:25.61,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gray?\N{\rCHT}葛雷？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.78,1:32:50.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me, Gray.\N{\rCHT}別丟下我 葛雷
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.12,1:32:54.56,ENG,,0,0,0,,I told Sid this was a one-way trip.\N{\rCHT}我告訴博士這次是有去無回了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.69,1:32:57.29,ENG,,0,0,0,,Looks like I was right.\N{\rCHT}看來我說對了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.64,1:32:59.96,ENG,,0,0,0,,No, Gray. Hang on, please.\N{\rCHT}不 你要撐下去
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.27,1:33:02.25,ENG,,0,0,0,,I still have the wave.\N{\rCHT}我仍有能量波
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.28,1:33:04.24,ENG,,0,0,0,,We can get through this.\N{\rCHT}我們撐的過去的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.28,1:33:11.98,ENG,,0,0,0,,- We're not gonna make it. - We're going to make it.\N{\rCHT}- 來不及了 - 來得及
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.98,1:33:14.30,ENG,,0,0,0,,We both know that isn't true.\N{\rCHT}我們都知道來不及了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.48,1:33:26.01,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gray...\N{\rCHT}葛雷…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.39,1:33:28.78,ENG,,0,0,0,,Help me.\N{\rCHT}扶我起來
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.72,1:33:38.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Gray...\N{\rCHT}葛雷…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.29,1:33:41.02,ENG,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.\N{\rCHT}聽我說
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.10,1:33:43.20,ENG,,0,0,0,,You saved my life once.\N{\rCHT}你救過我
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.56,1:33:45.80,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now I want you to save yourself. Gray,\N{\rCHT}現在我要你救自己 葛雷
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.80,1:33:47.48,ENG,,0,0,0,,no. Please.\N{\rCHT}不 求你了？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.48,1:33:50.99,ENG,,0,0,0,,Let me do this, Aki. Trust me.\N{\rCHT}讓我這麼做 阿琪 相信我
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.64,1:34:02.59,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me, Gray.\N{\rCHT}葛雷 別離開我
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.76,1:34:05.45,ENG,,0,0,0,,You've been trying to tell me that death isn't the end.\N{\rCHT}你一直說死亡並不是終結
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.45,1:34:07.42,ENG,,0,0,0,,Don't back out on me.\N{\rCHT}在我終於相信後
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.54,1:34:10.94,ENG,,0,0,0,,Now that I finally believe.\N{\rCHT}別說不是
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.24,1:34:24.04,ENG,,0,0,0,,I love you.\N{\rCHT}我愛你
